Package de.stocker.model.dataWrappers

Class DataProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.stocker.model.dataWrappers.DataProvider
  • public class DataProvider
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class DataProvider containing all relevant information for the network interface to connect to the data provider. A new instance of this class can also be created by user input in the preferences to add new data providers.
    Author:
    Matthias Rudolph
